Class FilterContainer

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.dmc.types.FilterContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class FilterContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The FilterContainer serves a similar purpose to the NameContainer but for DmcFilter derivatives. The container holds typed filter implementations and is used in the Dark Matter Protocol implementations of Requests that support filters.
